author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Wonderful stream today... :_ちょうちょ:

Again as Minecraft's update was the last stream of 2020, also became the 1st gameplay at 2021. :_きゅん:
This time with the same mission of obtaining these rare minerals, in various ocassions using the "Tsurupettachi Deluxe" (Special pickaxe mainly named "Tsurupettachi Kai" restored by Pekora-san) but some parts were the most hazardous, not only with the Magma falling and some filtrations... Also Endermen were there and attacked player's character. Rushia-daitenshi sheltered herself in fact of recovering stamina and buffing burning resistance.

But another problem was present... Not only because too many excavations using Trinitrotoluene (T.N.T.) and magma filtrations, also the major problem for Rushia: finding the Exit... Until she could find it. :_あせり:

Fortunately, she drank the burning buffer potion before, she already was falling from stone bridges and swimming into magma.

And the Supaachaato Orei Time was the strong point later of about 4 hours of adventure :_るんるん:

Nice for today... Rushia-daitenshi, fellow fandeads and all people, thank you very very very very much.
